RootTable.Filter: SELECT o.ea_guid AS CLASSGUID, o.object_type AS CLASSTYPE, o.object_type, o.name, o.note AS notes, o.createddate, o.modifieddate FROM t_object o WHERE o.package_id IN (#Branch#) AND NOT EXISTS ( SELECT * FROM t_diagramobjects INNER JOIN t_diagram ON t_diagramobjects.diagram_id = t_diagram.diagram_id WHERE t_diagram.package_id IN (#Branch#) AND t_diagramobjects.object_id = o.object_id); #DB=COMMENT# Find the objects that are not present on any diagram (in the selected package). #DB=COMMENT#
